---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
    title="404 – Halaman Tidak Ditemukan | Mitsubishi Sleman"
    description="Halaman yang Anda cari tidak ditemukan. Kembali ke beranda untuk melihat promo Mitsubishi terbaru di Sleman Yogyakarta."
>
    <div class="not-found-hero">
        <div class="not-found-inner">
            <div class="not-found-code">404</div>
            <h1>Halaman Tidak Ditemukan</h1>
            <p>Maaf, halaman yang Anda cari tidak ada atau telah dipindahkan.<br>
               Jangan khawatir, Putra siap membantu Anda menemukan mobil yang tepat!</p>

            <div class="not-found-actions">
                <a href="/" class="cta-btn">
                    <i class="fas fa-home"></i> Kembali ke Beranda
                </a>
                <a href="https://wa.me/628974362666?text=Halo%20Putra%2C%20saya%20butuh%20bantuan%20mencari%20informasi%20di%20website" 
                   class="cta-btn cta-btn--outline" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
                    <i class="fab fa-whatsapp"></i> Chat Putra
                </a>
            </div>

            <div class="not-found-links">
                <p>Atau langsung kunjungi halaman produk kami:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="/xpander-sleman.html">🚗 Harga Mitsubishi Xpander Sleman</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/pajero-sport-sleman.html">🚙 Harga Pajero Sport Sleman</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/xforce-jogja.html">🏎 Harga Xforce Jogja</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/dealer-mitsubishi-sleman.html">🏢 Info Dealer Mitsubishi Sleman</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>

<style>
.not-found-hero {
    margin-top: 68px;
    min-height: calc(100vh - 68px - 240px);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 4rem 20px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fafafa 0%, #fff5f5 100%);
}
.not-found-inner {
    max-width: 600px;
    text-align: center;
}
.not-found-code {
    font-size: 8rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--m-red);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    opacity: 0.15;
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    position: relative;
}
.not-found-inner h1 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: var(--m-black);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
}
.not-found-inner > p {
    color: var(--m-mid-grey);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
}
.not-found-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
}
.cta-btn--outline {
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--m-red);
    border: 2px solid var(--m-red);
}
.cta-btn--outline:hover {
    background: var(--m-red);
    color: white;
}
.not-found-links p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--m-mid-grey);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
}
.not-found-links ul {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 10px;
}
.not-found-links a {
    color: var(--m-red);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    transition: opacity 0.2s;
}
.not-found-links a:hover {
    opacity: 0.75;
    text-decoration: underline;
}
</style>
